# DIF-4 Deprecation Allowlist
# Format: regex pattern, one per line. Comments start with #.
# When a violation matches one of these, it's intentionally allowed.
#
# Rules:
#  - Every entry MUST include a justification comment above
#  - Re-evaluate quarterly: stale allowlist entries are themselves drift

# Streaming SSE response in chat-worker.js handleChatStream cannot use callAI
# (wrapper has no streaming support). Cost is logged post-stream via direct
# ai_calls INSERT. The hardcoded 'claude-sonnet-4-6' there is the streaming
# request body model. Allow this specific reference until callAI supports SSE.
chat-worker\.js:699:.*claude-sonnet-4-6
chat-worker\.js:782:.*claude-sonnet-4-6

# fetchWithBackoff health check in finance-audit-engine.js: pings Anthropic with
# custom retry semantics; failure trips read-only. Routing through callAI would
# conflate "budget blocked" with "API broken." Health check needs literal model id.
finance-audit-engine\.js:.*claude-haiku-4-5
